      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAKE'S DESIRE (8) has recorded back to back wins, last time scoring at this track over 330m by 4 lengths (19.05). Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Looks the one to beat. TIME FOR TEA (2) last start finished 4th over 330m at this track beaten 8 lengths (19.47) behind Model Fernanda in a Grade 5 on May 20. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts JACOBITE THORN (3) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 19.00 beating Landed. Won at her only start from this draw. Should feature again. EDGE OF FAITH (1) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten third (26.03) in a Grade 5 at this track last time out.",
